01:57:24.020 --> 01:57:26.690
to avoid getting sued to
research and make sure

01:57:26.690 --> 01:57:29.900
that they have a right
to use that song?

01:57:30.960 --> 01:57:33.490
&gt;&gt; Chaim Levinson: Well,
that is a very good question.

01:57:36.290 --> 01:57:38.300
Well, so during the
certification process,

01:57:38.300 --> 01:57:42.430
you would have a certificate
that's given to you.

01:57:42.430 --> 01:57:47.350 position:56%
And in the registration, it would
claim that that is indeed your work.

01:57:47.350 --> 01:57:50.420
What then happens is
that is transferred

01:57:50.420 --> 01:57:57.900
