copyright law will protect you
saying that this work belongs to you

01:58:17.680 --> 01:58:27.590
but it does not decide who it
belongs to but there is a process

01:58:27.590 --> 01:58:31.480
that would be made clear to
you what actually belongs

01:58:31.480 --> 01:58:33.780
to you in that situation.

01:58:33.780 --> 01:58:41.800
So, you don't really have to
be afraid of the ramifications,

01:58:41.800 --> 01:58:43.990
you can be confident
that any creative work

01:58:43.990 --> 01:58:47.700
that you make has been
recorded correctly

01:58:47.700 --> 01:58:54.560
and that we will protect
you through that.

01:58:54.560 --> 01:58:56.520
Any other questions
from the audience?

01:58:56.520 --> 01:58:59.970
Yeah? I love questions.

01:59:02.180 --> 01:59:05.750
&gt;&gt; So, I'm going to pick
