01:59:05.750 --> 01:59:07.410 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Chaim Levinson: Yeah, no worries.

01:59:07.410 --> 01:59:09.880
&gt;&gt; So, for a copyright--

01:59:14.910 --> 01:59:17.360
