01:59:42.080 --> 01:59:43.450
&gt;&gt; Chaim Levinson: Right.

01:59:43.450 --> 01:59:45.620 position:56%
So you actually have to record that.

01:59:45.620 --> 01:59:49.960
You have to put it down on some
