01:59:49.960 --> 01:59:53.490
when you're finished with
the work at that moment is

01:59:53.490 --> 01:59:58.140
when it becomes protected
under copyright.

01:59:58.140 --> 02:00:01.940
&gt;&gt; OK. So, you're saying, in order
