reputable person at that time.

03:14:28.420 --> 03:14:32.170
And so, he brought Mason Fitch
Cogswell under his tutelage.

03:14:32.170 --> 03:14:37.950
And he was a very brilliant man.

03:14:37.950 --> 03:14:43.000
