03:21:18.040 --> 03:21:19.440
Laurent Clerc?

03:21:19.440 --> 03:21:25.190
You know, many of the younger
generation don't know who Clerc is

03:21:25.190 --> 03:21:27.950
which is really a travesty.

03:21:27.950 --> 03:21:30.690
That falls on the job--

03:21:30.690 --> 03:21:34.310
the job falls on people
like yourself and me.

03:21:34.310 --> 03:21:36.990
We need to keep on
teaching deaf history.

03:21:36.990 --> 03:21:43.130
We can't forget people in our
heritage like Laurent Clerc.

03:21:43.130 --> 03:21:48.500
He, Cogswell, Thomas
Hopkins Gallaudet,

03:21:48.500 --> 03:21:52.330
