take 90 days to seashore?

03:36:44.960 --> 03:36:55.320
With the wind picking up, it gave
us hope to take less than 90 days.

03:36:55.320 --> 03:37:01.180
July 2nd. Now, it's
our second month.

03:37:17.170 --> 03:37:21.550
On July 3rd, going about my
normal routine in the morning,

03:37:21.550 --> 03:37:24.470
